  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Improve educational achievement through increased school attendance, especially of girls, through solar energy, by: 1. Improving sanitary facilities by using photovoltaic systems to heat water.2. Providing nutritious diet at school through establishing bio-gardens with solar tents. solar pumping irrigation powered by photovoltaic systems to grow crops. 3. Implementing sustainable management whereby the communities are trained in operating and maintaining the solar equipment.</narrative>
